  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "So it came to pass, when all the men of war were consumed,.... By wasting diseases and judgments of one kind or another: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and dead from among the people; the rising and surviving generation. ",
        "children": [
